title: Dick Tracy
actors: Ralph Byrd, Kay Hughes, Smiley Burnette, Lee Van Atta, John Picorri, Carleton Young, Fred Hamilton, Francis X. Bushman, John Dilson, Richard Beach, Wedgwood Nowell, Theodore Lorch, Edwin Stanley, Harrison Greene, Herbert Weber
description: A master criminal called The Spider puts the famous detective's brother under a hypnotic spell and turns him against Dick.
